    <title>微信公众号开发（二）消息接收与响应</title>
    <url>/2022/04/22/%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%85%AC%E4%BC%97%E5%8F%B7/2.%20%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%85%AC%E4%BC%97%E5%8F%B7%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E6%8E%A5%E6%94%B6%E4%B8%8E%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="一、消息接收过程"><a href="#一、消息接收过程" class="headerlink" title="一、消息接收过程"></a>一、消息接收过程</h2><p><a href="https://developers.weixin.qq.com/doc/offiaccount/Message_Management/Receiving_standard_messages.html">参考文档</a></p>
<p>当普通微信用户向公众账号发消息时，微信服务器将 POST 消息的 XML 数据包到开发者填写的 URL 上。</p>
<p>此前，对于我们填写的 URL ，我们已经设置了一个处理 GET 请求的<code>Controller</code>，该请求用于验证服务器的有效性。</p>
<p>下面，我们需要再设置一个处理 GET 请求<code>Controller</code>来处理微信服务器转发过来的用户消息。</p>
<ol>
<li>首先创建一个实体类，封装接收的<code>xml</code>数据</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@XmlRootElement(name = &quot;xml&quot;)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@XmlAccessorType(XmlAccessType.FIELD)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@ToString</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Data</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Component</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">InMessage</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> String FromUserName;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">protected</span> String ToUserName;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">protected</span> Long CreateTime;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">protected</span> String MsgType;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">protected</span> Long MsgId;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> String Content;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>由于接收到的数据是 xml 格式，所以需要添加<code>@XmlRootElement</code> 和 <code>@XmlAccessorType</code> 两个注解来解析</p>
<ol start="2">
<li><p>创建处理 POST 请求的<code>Controller</code></p>
<p>首先打印一下接收到的数据</p>
</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">   <span class="meta">@PostMapping(&quot;/&quot;)</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="meta">@ResponseBody</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="keyword">public</span> Object <span class="title function_">handleMessage</span><span class="params">(<span class="meta">@RequestBody</span> InMessage msg)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">       System.out.println(msg.toString());</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>​        然后关注测试号，发送消息进行验证</p>
<p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunHy98/img/main/202206261655394.png" alt="image-20220626165548261"></p>
<p>​        查看服务端的打印结果，各字段的含义见<a href="https://developers.weixin.qq.com/doc/offiaccount/Message_Management/Receiving_standard_messages.html">参考文档</a></p>
<p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunHy98/img/main/202206261657381.png" alt="image-20220626165703348"></p>
<ol start="3">
<li>上面，服务端已经接收到了微信服务器转发过来的消息。我们可以自定义返回的消息，来回复用户。</li>
</ol>
<p>   首先创建一个实体类，封装响应的<code>xml</code>数据</p>
<p>   响应消息不用设置<code>MsgId</code></p>
   <figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@XmlRootElement(name = &quot;xml&quot;)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@XmlAccessorType(XmlAccessType.FIELD)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@ToString</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Data</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Component</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">OutMessage</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> String FromUserName;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">protected</span> String ToUserName;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">protected</span> Long CreateTime;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">protected</span> String MsgType;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> String Content;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>   然后设置响应的消息，此时需要在<code>@PostMapping</code>上添加<code>produces= &#123;MediaType.TEXT_XML_VALUE&#125;</code>，否则会响应失败</p>
   <figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@PostMapping(value = &quot;/&quot;, produces= &#123;MediaType.TEXT_XML_VALUE&#125;)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@ResponseBody</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> Object <span class="title function_">handleMessage</span><span class="params">(<span class="meta">@RequestBody</span> InMessage msg)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">OutMessage</span> <span class="variable">outMessage</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">OutMessage</span>();</span><br><span class="line">    outMessage.setToUserName(msg.getFromUserName());</span><br><span class="line">    outMessage.setFromUserName(msg.getToUserName());</span><br><span class="line">    outMessage.setMsgType(msg.getMsgType());</span><br><span class="line">    outMessage.setCreateTime(System.currentTimeMillis()/<span class="number">1000</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    outMessage.setContent(msg.getContent());</span><br><span class="line">    System.out.println(msg);</span><br><span class="line">    System.out.println(outMessage);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> outMessage;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">   </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ol start="4">
<li>测试号进行测试</li>
</ol>
<p>   <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunHy98/img/main/202206261742821.png" alt="image-20220626174252777"></p>
]]></content>
